---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="tiempo-profundo"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 overflow-hidden"
>
    
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center transition-transform duration-100 ease-linear"
        id="landscape-mover"
    >
        <div
            class="w-[300vw] h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1c1917] via-[#292524] to-[#0c0a09] flex items-center justify-around opacity-50"
        >
            <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 rounded-full bg-[#44403c] blur-3xl opacity-30">
            </div>
            <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 rounded-full bg-[#57534e] blur-3xl opacity-30">
            </div>
            <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 rounded-full bg-[#292524] blur-3xl opacity-30">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
    <div class="w-full relative" id="section1-container">
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
                <span
                    class="trigo-chapter text-amber-600/60 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4"
                    >El Tiempo Profundo</span
                >
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#e7e5e4]">
                    200.000 Años de Silencio
                </h2>

                <div
                    class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8 backdrop-blur-sm bg-black/30 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg border border-stone-800/50 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
                >
                    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#d6d3d1]">
                        Durante el 99% de nuestra historia, fuimos nómadas. El mundo no nos
                        pertenecía; nosotros pertenecíamos al mundo.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#a8a29e]">
                        Cazábamos, recolectábamos, y seguíamos adelante. La vida era peligrosa, sí,
                        pero era ligera. <ShareableQuote
                            quote="No teníamos dueños, ni muros, ni dioses enfadados."
                        />
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
